{"tid":1199430,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實9月12日我地根本唔應該出去","createTime":"2019-06-10T13:11:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T13:26:33.000Z","uid":189746,"like":3,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5ce4caf8273ead67e2a0b58cd4cc58ab9c056543","tid":1199430,"uid":189746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T13:11:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">星期日有去現場或者有睇直播日嘅 應該感覺到成個遊行係一盤散沙 就算夜晚爆發沖突，一支警犬黎到就已經比人反cup<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n9月12日阻止二讀通過基本上係香港最後一役 個日沖突一定會不斷升級 但係去到依家都仲未有一套指揮系統 有效咁組織成個行動 有計劃咁佔領又好 做咩都好 若然當日又好似星期日咁 比多一倍人你又點<br />\n<br />\n我地唔似外國咁玩暴力 個個人都係武裝單位 <br />\n而團結同組織係我地唯一武器 亦係最強力量 所以我地好需求一套戰揮 控制成個大局！<br />\n<br />\n真心為香港好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望最後一戰係我地反cup <br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HsK1pqa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHsK1pqa.png&h=f8383042&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0fc0898a194832cce14994efc26ddd8782e371cb","tid":1199430,"uid":189746,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T13:16:07.000Z","msg":"打錯 6月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22f57d3d5f2370d240a753ddd9137fa3755ad807","tid":1199430,"uid":185066,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T13:24:14.000Z","msg":"9月12號 可能香港已經變左死城<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"578dba0765da4241074694a472de172686a28050","tid":1199430,"uid":171786,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T13:25:17.000Z","msg":"9月12<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef4f927bd3881cb6b68fdb31946e3c752d7d627a","tid":1199430,"uid":345,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T13:25:57.000Z","msg":"咁9月12又真係未必出嚟嘅 咁遠嘅事"},{"pid":"c942bfc33848d54a826f938bf9b28a42957fbc70","tid":1199430,"uid":7516,"like":1